(
<bibRefCitation author="Fernandez F." box="[534,733,1930,1956]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" pagination="128 - 145" refId="ref3855" refString="Fernandez F. 2007. Two new South American species of Monomorium Mayr with taxonomic notes on the genus. In: Snelling R. R., Fisher B. L &amp; Ward P. S. (eds) Advances in Ant Systematics (Hymenoptera: Formicidae): Homage to E. O. Wilson - 50 Years of Contributions. Memoirs of the American Entomological Institute 80: 128 - 145." type="journal article" year="2007">Fernández, 2007</bibRefCitation>
