</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[750,883,1930,1956]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" rank="species">comb. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, worker from Benjamin Constant, Amazon, Brazil (ICN). SEM photographs. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[573,594,1965,1991]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">A</emphasis>
. Head in full face view. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[871,891,1965,1991]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">B</emphasis>
